title: TEMPLATE Miniature red English phone booth in 1:12 scale | PDF
description: To make the miniature phone booth, you will need• Modeling plastic sheet (0.5 mm thick)• Plastic model glue• Tacky Glue• Red acrylic paint• Brown soft pastel• Self-adhesive paper• Clear plastic sheet The price includes 1 PDF file with one sheet of templates and detailed assembly instructions.The finished phone booth shown in the photos is for demonstration purposes only.Please note that the diagram is made at a 1:12 scale and cannot be enlarged without losing image quality.…
